        <abstract> 
<p>Feels that StGJM’s review of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Q. Rev.</hi> 131 (1871): 47–90] greatly misrepresents CD’s opinions and conclusions. Feels their differences of opinion are so great that discussion of almost any subject would be a waste of both their time.</p> 
